OL,3,CCold weather snap has 'deepened'
OL,4,Chomelessness crisis, says charity
OL,6,FA homelessness charity has told UTV
OL,7,Fthat the recent spell of sub-zero
OL,8,Ftemperatures has 'deepened' the crisis
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FAround 30 people availed of an
OL,12,Fovernight drop-in service ran by the
OL,13,FWelcome Organisation in Belfast city
OL,14,Fcentre on Thursday night.
OL,16,FDuring filming with the charity,
OL,17,Ftemperatures in the city hit -2
OL,18,Fdegrees celsius.
