OL,3,CCold weather snap has 'deepened'
OL,4,Chomelessness crisis, says charity
OL,6,FThe Housing Executive's Severe Weather
OL,7,FEmergency Protocols (SWEP) were in
OL,8,Fplace in a bid to help all rough
OL,9,Fsleepers.
OL,11,FSleeping mats and sleeping bags were
OL,12,Fprovided at St Mary's Church with tea,
OL,13,Fcoffee and drinks also on offer to a
OL,14,Fcommunity who face the brunt of
OL,15,Ffreezing conditions more than anyone.
OL,17,F"It's not glamorous, it's not
OL,18,Fmassively comfortable but it is
OL,19,Fpotentially life-saving," said Ellie
OL,20,FHippsley, Street Outreach Manager with
OL,21,Fthe Welcome Organisation.
