OL,3,CCold weather snap has 'deepened'
OL,4,Chomelessness crisis, says charity
OL,6,FUTV spoke to one homeless man who
OL,7,Fwanted to remain anonymous.
OL,9,F27-year-old 'Adam', not his real name,
OL,10,Fsaid that he wanted to find a
OL,11,Fpermanent home but was struggling to
OL,12,Fdo so.
OL,14,F"I can't sort my life out when I have
OL,15,Fnowhere permanent to stay," he said.
OL,17,FBoth his mother and father have died.
