OL,3,CCold weather snap has 'deepened'
OL,4,Chomelessness crisis, says charity
OL,6,FThe hall in St Mary's is being used by
OL,7,Fthe charity after it had to leave it's
OL,8,Fformer premises on Townsend Street in
OL,9,Fthe city last year. Mats were laid out
OL,10,Fside-by-side along with a sleeping bag.
OL,12,FPeople of different ages, different
OL,13,Fnationalities and various complex
OL,14,Fneeds sought shelter to escape the
OL,15,Fcold.
OL,17,FPastor Christopher Tripp brought
OL,18,Fhomeless people to the temporary
OL,19,Fshelter on Thursday. He walks around
OL,20,Fthe city offering help to people who
OL,21,Freally need it.
