OL,3,CCold weather snap has 'deepened'
OL,4,Chomelessness crisis, says charity
OL,6,F"You just have to be patient, work
OL,7,Fwith them (homeless people) bit by
OL,8,Fbit, just a little here, a little
OL,9,Fthere in small steps, baby steps until
OL,10,Fyou see them come to a place where
OL,11,Fthey really start to care for
OL,12,Fthemselves.
OL,14,F"The problem here isn't homelessness,"
OL,15,Fhe told UTV. "It's hopelessness," he
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FThe weather may now start to change
OL,19,Fover the next few days, but it will
OL,20,Ftake much longer to address a crisis
OL,21,Flike this.
